data.description: Beautifully updated home with hardwood and tile floors throughout  main level, hardwood in master bedroom, kitchen with granite and stainless steel appliances, sunroom out of  kitchen walks out to the deck, master bathroom with granite countertop and frameless shower, upgraded tiles. Finished basement walks out to patio. Fenced back yard with a shed.
